  "title": "[ OFFICE HOUR! ] AD HOC FLEXI Locum Staff Nurse (Day Surgery / Day Ward ) West $29/hr #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Jurong<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Locum (3 Months)<br /><strong>Rate:</strong> $29 per hour</p><h3><strong>Working Hours</strong></h3><ul><li>Monday to Friday, office hours</li><li>8:00 a.m. – 5:30 p.m.</li><li>Engagement initially on an ad-hoc basis; consistent scheduling may be offered based on performance</li></ul><h3><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Provide nursing support for day surgery and operating theatre procedures</li><li>Perform scrub duties during surgical and endoscopy procedures</li><li>Assist in pre-operative and post-operative patient care</li><li>Support operating theatre workflows and infection control standards</li><li>Ensure safe handling of surgical instruments and equipment</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>Valid SNB registration</li><li>Experience in scrub duties is strongly preferred</li><li>Familiarity with endoscopy procedures is advantageous</li><li>Able to commit to the locum period and flexible scheduling</li></ul><p>All qualified applicants, please click “ APPLY NOW”<br /></p><p>Or you may send in your resume to:</p><p>Whatsapp: https://wa.me/+6589530688 </p><p>Email : <a href=\"mailto:kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</a><br /></p><p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p>",
